---
/**
 * About Page - Who I Am
 */
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Ashton.com.au"
  description="About Ashton Turner - Security consultant and systems engineer based in Sydney."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16">
    <article class="space-y-8">
      {/* Header */}
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">about</h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">a bit more about me</p>
      </div>

      {/* Main Content - Narrative Style */}
      <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          i grew up on the central coast of australia, spending way too much
          time on computers. that obsession turned into a career — first at <span
            class="text-white">google</span
          >, then <span class="text-white">apple</span>, before bouncing around
          MSPs, healthcare IT, and telco for the better part of a decade.
        </p>

        <p>
          somewhere along the way i got curious about security. not in a "i'm a
          l33t hacker" way — more like "let me see if i can poke holes in this."
          still learning, but i've been picking up pentesting, playing CTFs, and
          hunting bugs on hackerone when i get the chance.
        </p>

        <p>
          these days i work on a mix of infrastructure and security stuff. when
          i'm not at the keyboard, you'll find me training muay thai, listening
          to too much music, or occasionally touching grass.
        </p>

        <p>and yes, i did overpay for this domain.</p>

        {/* Contact */}
        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-white/5 space-y-2">
          <p>
            security inquiries →{" "}
            <a
              href="mailto:security@ashton.com.au"
              class="text-primary hover:underline"
            >
              security@ashton.com.au
            </a>
          </p>
          <p>
            everything else →{" "}
            <a
              href="mailto:hello@ashton.com.au"
              class="text-primary hover:underline"
            >
              hello@ashton.com.au
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
